                        <div class="hidden">A google drive knockoff made using React and Express.</div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://auth.gruzservices.com" target="_blank">
                        <p>Authentication</p>
                        <div class="hidden">The one stop authenticator for all my apps. Written in Svelte, TypeScript, Sqlite and TypeORM.</div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://small.gruzservices.com" target="_blank">
                        <p>Small</p>
                        <div class="hidden">Projects that are too small for its own subdomain.</div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://files.gruzservices.com" target="_blank">
                        <p>Storage V2</p>
                        <div class="hidden">
                            Currently under development. Uses Svelte instead of React for speed.
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="about">
            <div class="about-img-part">
                <img src="/info.svg" alt="Info Icon">
            </div>
            <div class="about-text-part">
                <div class="about-text-part-box">
                    <h3>About Me</h3>
                    <p>
                        Hi. I'm Stephen. I currently in 12th grade and want to become a software developer. This website is the hub of all my projects. This is where I can display my skills as both a frontend and backend developer. I have a <span><a href="https://github.com/Stephen10121" target="_blank">Github Account</a></span> that holds most of the code for my projects. If you want to contact me, <span><a href="#contact">click here.</a></span>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="extra">
                    <h3>What I use</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Python</li>
                        <li>Javascript</li>
                        <li>TypeScript</li>
                        <li>C/Arduino</li>
                        <li>Express</li>
                        <li>Flask</li>
                        <li>Svelte</li>
                        <li>React</li>
